Lift

Find cannabis product

I worked as a Full Stack MERN Developer and there were 8 devs on this team.

Overall, there are sub apps - for users, admin and api. I created pixel perfect pages from the designs on Invision using React.JS and implemented state management using Redux and API integration using Redux Saga. Also, I contributed to the back end development using Node.js, Mongoose, Express.js, Redis. Furthermore, I implemented integration with various third party services such as SurveyGizmo, ActiveCampaign, GTM, Cron Jobs, Cohesion DB, Neilson DMP, etc.

I implemented several functionalities as following.

- Created Age Gate Interface
    The user must be the age of majority in his province(19+, or 18+ in Alberta or 21+ in Quebec)

- Created Homepage
    Created several efficient Components for Review Card, Product card, Article Card, Main menu, etc.
    Search matching products and article data and show them on homepage.

- Created Products List Page
    You can sort/filter products stored in Data by using several parameters such as most popular or recent, product type, THC & CBD, Plant type, effect.

- Created Product Individual Page
    You can see the information about individual product including business information, reviews, effects felt, activities used for, top method of consumption, Scents and so on.

- Created Accessory List page and individual page
    You can sort/filter the accessories stored in Data and look into the individual accessory information.

- Created Brands List page and individual page
    You can sort/filter the businesses stored in Data and look into the individual business information.
